-- U.K. Pound Declines Against Dollar, Euro As Inflation Slows
-- B y   L u k a n y o   M n y a n d a
-- 2012-06-19T08:41:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-19/u-k-pound-declines-against-dollar-euro-as-inflation-slows.html
The U.K. pound stayed lower against
the dollar and the euro as a report showed inflation
unexpectedly slowed last month.  Sterling was 0.2 percent lower at $1.5635 at 9:37 a.m.
 London , and depreciated by 0.3 percent against the 17-nation
euro to 80.48 pence.    To contact the reporter on this story:
Lukanyo Mnyanda in Edinburgh at 
